OL,3,CFormer American Express staff feel
OL,4,C'betrayed' pension hasn't risen by
OL,5,Cinflation
OL,7,FFormer employees of American Express
OL,8,Fsay they feel "betrayed" by the
OL,9,Fcompany, as it has not been increasing
OL,10,Ftheir pensions by inflation.
OL,12,FChristine Mucklestone, from Burgess
OL,13,FHill, in West Sussex, worked for the
OL,14,Fmulti-billion pound bank holding
OL,15,Fcompany for 25 years, splitting that
OL,16,Ftime between Brighton and Phoenix,
OL,17,FArizona.
