OL,3,CFormer American Express staff feel
OL,4,C'betrayed' pension hasn't risen by
OL,5,Cinflation
OL,7,FShe now estimates the real value of
OL,8,Fher pension has dropped 40% since Amex
OL,9,Fstopped increasing it each year by
OL,10,Finflation.
OL,12,FMs Mucklestone said: "It's a betrayal,
OL,13,FI feel betrayed. Safety net is a good
OL,14,Fword because that is what I thought I
OL,15,Fhad in that pension because at the
OL,16,Ftime, it was considered a basic full-
OL,17,Ftime salary.
OL,19,F"I thought I would be okay in my
OL,20,Fretirement years and now, I am not."
