OL,7,FAnother former employee, David
OL,8,FMorling, from Shoreham-by-Sea, also in
OL,9,FWest Sussex, estimates that he is
OL,10,Faround #700 light, per month, compared
OL,11,Fto where he was ten years ago.
OL,13,FMr Morling said: "I think there is a
OL,14,Fgreat sense of dismay. They say that
OL,15,Fthey wouldn't be able to do this
OL,16,Fwithout their employees, but they are
OL,17,Fforgetting about the employees of the
OL,18,F70s, 80s and 90s.
