OL,3,CFormer American Express staff feel
OL,4,C'betrayed' pension hasn't risen by
OL,5,Cinflation
OL,7,F"We have been left neglected and we
OL,8,Fhave seen the value of our pension
OL,9,Fbeen eroded."
OL,11,FCompanies are not legally required to
OL,12,Fincrease pension payouts in line with
OL,13,Finflation for those who worked for the
OL,14,Fbusiness before April 1997, with any
OL,15,Fincreases before then at the
OL,16,Fdiscretion of the company.
OL,18,FHowever, under pension law, any
OL,19,Femployees hired after April 1997, must
OL,20,Fhave their pension topped up in line
OL,21,Fwith inflation.
