OL,7,FThe last time American Express paid
OL,8,Fthe discretionary difference was in
OL,9,F2014, despite the company reporting
OL,10,Frecord revenues of $65.9 billion last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThe campaign groups say thousands of
OL,14,Fformer employees are affected.
OL,16,FAn American Express spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"American Express complies with all
OL,18,Fits pension obligations to current and
OL,19,Fformer colleagues and will continue to
OL,20,Fdo so in the future.
